subdivision_of_building: The proposed site is between Blocks 4 and 5 with demolition required of a single storey extension to Block 4 to ensure the extension can be complete. The extension itself will impact the existing ground, first and roof of Block 5.
description: Demolish existing single storey extension to Block 4.  New three storey side extension to Block 5 to provide additional theatres, staff welfare and store.  (sumary)
decision_conditions:
The development hereby permitted shall be begun no later than the  expiration of three years from the date of this permission.

Reason: In order to comply with the requirements of Section 91 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
